覺得d人分得太散，d人覺得人少，就會散....<br />\n<br />\n而且，依家每日資訊太多，一日搞太多地區的遊行，一定有d係被忽視左，咁又好浪費大家的努力<br />\n<br />\n所以，有d遊行會因為個日太多不同地方的遊行撞期，避免分薄人數而取消，但係佢本身又宣傳左好耐，令到件事好尷尬咁？我1999.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c31ecfb776a726a494f3a69cb94f714fa8fcfd5","tid":1438030,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"33bc4971754cd76e607b6c8a00b7d803f49337cd","tid":1438030,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e8f69b5567ecd266000efdd4f893a3c36579ef6","tid":1438030,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"177c84f29edb6038dd6e584cfdba3f82cba3d6ff","tid":1438030,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:51:27.000Z","msg":"唔割席唔係唔用腦嘅籍口，我希望每一次改期都需要經過慎重嘅考慮，唔係人云亦云"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"所以 佢就係慎重考慮完先要同大眾講取消 明未<br />\n<br />\n聽日理撚得你去大埔定機場 <br />\n去大埔嘅自己小心 記住<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">be water</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地要睇嘅得呢一句：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">宇宙大爆炸都唔撚割！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:54:15.000Z","msg":"我冇野要同你講"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"我明你有你嘅主張 但每個人都會思考 當機立斷最緊要<br />\n而家唔取消都取消咗 唯有諗下一步點做<br />\n總之我得一句 宇宙大爆炸都唔撚割！"},{"pid":"438463e0eb8a1b3a29dbea5a8b9e7e7888acaf49","tid":1438030,"uid":41901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c31ecfb776a726a494f3a69cb94f714fa8fcfd5","tid":1438030,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"33bc4971754cd76e607b6c8a00b7d803f49337cd","tid":1438030,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e8f69b5567ecd266000efdd4f893a3c36579ef6","tid":1438030,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,