moji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"點解？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"Um....我估依家同一日最多可以容納到3個遊行<br />\neg. 今個星期六(8月10)有機埸，沙田，大埔，(原本的黃大仙)<br />\n公布左的地點係用黎集合人數，太多地點d人就太分散，令在埸人士覺得民氣不足<br />\n同埋，依家集合左一區的人係會轉場周圍走，每走一次就會少左d人，太多地方舉行遊行，會覺得d人分得太散，d人覺得人少，就會散....<br />\n<br />\n而且，依家每日資訊太多，一日搞太多地區的遊行，一定有d係被忽視左，咁又好浪費大家的努力<br />\n<br />\n所以，有d遊行會因為個日太多不同地方的遊行撞期，避免分薄人數而取消，但係佢本身又宣傳左好耐，令到件事好尷尬咁？我1999.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"用正向思維諗，每次狗都唔可以正確預測示威者嘅人數，同日開花佢地嘅成本先係最大，如果人數真係不足，一係call馬，一係臨時轉場，但係比活生生握殺一個遊行好一百萬倍，集中一個地方係益左佢"},{"pid":"82011e9905bb131322bc27f7aed19484d8f8bcc6","tid":1438030,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:05:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同我推一千萬次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唇亡齒寒，和理勇武缺一不可。</span></span>"},{"pid":"1581163e6fa6f17f4583ef57a972b91251e2076b","tid":1438030,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"求下你地"},{"pid":"d42c7a8a9a0ba3f68bc5c5e553aa884f9213b4b7","tid":1438030,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"睇po唔好淨係睇頭一兩樓"},{"pid":"49653f7b8bef5c1be354c0f2fdad8fe3edca66e9","tid":1438030,"uid":228092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"阻一阻大家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/moJ6sY2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmoJ6sY2.jpg&h=59f607b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTmS7Y2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTmS7Y2.png&h=67416cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctnbD5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctnbD5H.jpg&h=1f1b63c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zwVMsY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzwVMsY3.jpg&h=ac3691f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuFgQco.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuFgQco.jpg&h=b2911e63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55f5d2faa431a68b2582ddd3c165c4e111a04535","tid":1438030,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8784f0c8c799d0d675590e3601431a7ee4d86e6f","tid":1438030,"uid":26637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"59fcf339921d0aeac5d709cf05f42f8a340221fd","tid":1438030,"uid":265443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8422c4dd742102488088eacdf6af86c281b918d0","tid":1438030,"uid":26637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"不可憤而興兵<br />\n你去港島東都係為啖氣 同五大訴求邊個訴求掛勾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:37:21.000Z","msg":"每一個遊行集會都好重要因爲每一次都係發聲嘅機會，唔係為啖氣，你當搞手係咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:42:17.000Z","msg":"我認同每一個都係發聲嘅機會<br />\n但係呢一個發聲嘅機會值唔值得令你星期日一定要响港島東岀現<br />\n<br />\n就係要珍惜每一個機會 先要權衡輕重 去揀一個風險較低嘅方案 即係轉日子 唔係一定要8月11號去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:09:49.000Z","msg":"每一個日子都有佢嘅風險，你取消左個遊行縱觀黎講邊個最得益？"},{"pid":"136deee99c7635391b07783b3aa91eb1f21d9620","tid":1438030,"uid":215811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"去第二度啦"},{"pid":"d522a2f37354b4b5ffcfb78f1959cbb0a098e412","tid":1438030,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"136deee99c7635391b07783b3aa91eb1f21d9620","tid":1438030,"uid":215811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"去第二度啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:12:36.000Z","msg":"你有一套完善可行嘅方案，可以，請講，唔好隨隨便便"},{"pid":"7d0bae8c077ca561b7f93a33ba1ef81f3c3978fe","tid":14